Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壞球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯的說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投不進好球區呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平均球速也只有80公里的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你們這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓咪們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能暫停一會兒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡會被踩到  會被壓扁的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能別讓貓腳玷污了這神聖的操場？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐佐佐佐美！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是笹瀨川佐佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅是女子壘球部閃耀的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是校內第一的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是鈴的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂操場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為那些目標崇高  不斷揮灑汗水的運動員準備的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是為了你們這些沒有目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天和貓混在一起的人們所準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且是以比賽為目標的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直是怎麼樣都行的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話真是怎麼樣都行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是在角落裡偷玩一下投接球的話也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的忍耐已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了我們壘球部能夠練習  把地方讓出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種想法倒是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗鈴  你竟敢羞辱我們壘球部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢對佐佐美大人玉足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手塚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許欺負小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來把貓帶進操場的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和鈴來一對一比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你勝了  我們就從操場離開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是若鈴勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:02:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要為自己後輩的所作所為道歉  並回去老實練習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本小姐怎麼可能會輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球  擊球手出局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的只是陪她玩一下投球練習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  已經這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽下次再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐美大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,130公里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為貓咪被欺負而認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像是緊急關頭的怪力一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼重視它們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先給剛才的魔球起個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是直球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面寄宿了貓的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷神喵喵球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你別閃著星星眼說這話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:56.94,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(320,332,320,325,0,900)\fad(900,0)}鈴習得了雷神喵喵球！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右右左  右右…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右右左  右右左
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  接下來看誰會上當
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要來嗎  手塚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右右左
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右右左…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一位挑戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經玩過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒嬌也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心軟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  是理樹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是信  好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次會是什麼課題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾會收到不可思議的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經是第三封了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是誰出於什麼目的送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然寫著如果完成全部的課題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會告訴我們世界的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要去做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好奇秘密是什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治好2-A1號的相思病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是夠俗氣的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  你知道什麼是相思病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相思病…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想死的病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確有人會想死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對不對  是說戀愛的相思病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種病…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是重症嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2-A應該是指班別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1號是學號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1號應該是男生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過會兒去找找他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找不認識的男生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗同學和直枝同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是2-A的1號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫相川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子讓我找好久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼像壞人來找碴似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都一樣是二年級  不用這麼拘謹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK  有啥事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  這種話不能說出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在患有相思病  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  為…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用多說  我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事前早有調查過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有調查過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就當我有眼線就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  你有什麼症狀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你問來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們替你治好這個病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出來也會輕鬆一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  我們會保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  請別跟其他人說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她在我面前  這裡就揪心的痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習也學不進去  上課時滿腦子都是她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定這是初戀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方是怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習運動文武雙全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還很有人望  是個很厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這樣的人完全配不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說還真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  還沒向她告白的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告白什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是失敗會很悲慘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所作為就放棄不會更懊悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底  對方是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  知道對方是誰也方便我們提建議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想說的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…笹瀨川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在這裡聽到她的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不是你問我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我沒有問那傢伙的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  你是問了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  也就是說相川君的心上人是笹瀨川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  這到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  平靜下來  冷靜想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是吶  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越是想要冷靜就越是會混亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  他不是說那人學習運動文武雙全還很有人望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所知道的佐佐佐佐佐美可不是那樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不能現在去破壞他的夢想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的問題不在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  也對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  你們還挺配的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她身後不是總跟著幾個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定能成為其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是只能當朋友的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  應該比這更慘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話  我跟她挺熟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該能給你們牽個線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼連理樹也在驚嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你準備如何去給他們牽線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會兒要在我房間開個茶會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想邀請小鈴也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  我覺得能聽到不少主意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹也去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅決不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能自己吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼聽話地過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  我十分高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想問問大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請儘管問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…如何才能…兩情相悅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴有心上人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜蜜蜜的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方是誰  是大姐姐我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說我  是讓其他人兩情相悅的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝同學和恭介同學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們之間有著深深的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍的人不用特意去為他們操心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如說操心反而會打擾他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是在圖書館裡伸手想要拿同一本書的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人大喊著要遲到了要遲到了在拐角撞一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛便開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混進去不少亂七八糟的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹覺得怎麼做比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問問她的愛好和喜歡的類型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問了之後怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是告訴相川君啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他應該很想更多地瞭解自己的心上人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗鈴  從剛才開始一直嘰嘰咕咕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話先說在前頭  之前那事沒門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  話說回來你有什麼愛好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,週末的時候在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一上來就問了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你問這些東西有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想要拿來當作我的笑柄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是拿來當笑柄的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是  想更深地瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能更加親密一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與叫佐瀨川佐佐美的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是在耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想要問什麼來著  愛好和什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,週末你都在做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有理想中的男生是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外貌啊性格之類的  希望你能詳細地告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼特別的愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,週末要練習壘球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理想中的男士是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍道部的宮澤大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謙吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渣渣美她喜歡謙吾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道該怎麼去和相川君說  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  先問問謙吾他怎麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就到這地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼一回事  你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你問我怎麼看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之前  你認識笹瀨川同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認識倒是認識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎麼的總是會在走廊裡和她碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都會和我打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她倒是在試著接近謙吾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我怎麼回答才能讓你們結束這個話題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是「我沒那個意思」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣滿意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謙吾他沒那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮澤同學他怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是有關笹瀨川同學的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說喜歡的對象是謙吾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事  他好像受了不小的打擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說他身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明顯是前者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是大驚小怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謙吾他沒那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對你來說不正好是個機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說謙吾的魅力是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先試著考慮一下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謙吾雖然塊頭很大很嚇人  對人也不怎麼親切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的魅力就是他的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解釋成很有男子漢氣概的話也還行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒謙吾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是夠跳躍的思維
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在渣渣美面前把那個強大的謙吾給打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就一定會迷上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不怎麼運動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是打不贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就培養相同的愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹瀨川同學不是沒什麼愛好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要提一些可能相同的愛好就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫畫和遊戲之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去不太能和她相同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音樂之類的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼經常聽的音樂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hip Hop吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Desktop電腦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一個音是相同的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借她幾張你喜歡的CD如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就借CD？  難度也太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就唱出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在原創的歌詞之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱含著對渣渣美秘密的愛慕之情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的那句歌詞記住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「笹瀨川佐佐美  就是你」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  Mission Start！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey you hey you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You you come on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Check it  現在  check it  現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹瀨川你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬舌頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想吵架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有挽回的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒謙吾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說  我是打不過的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  不偷襲的話確實打不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點卑鄙  也只能這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此  還是感覺打不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  就來個偷襲乘3吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘3？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我假裝摔倒  滑到謙吾的腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來  謙吾一定會跳著躲開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴裡說著「A套餐久等了」把餐盤砸向謙吾的後腦勺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣他一定會抱著頭蹲在地上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時你就一邊大喊「宮澤謙吾受死吧」一邊一腳踢上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得就算踢一腳上去也沒什麼用…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就使盡渾身解數衝過去踢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從兩百米開外助跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這走廊還真夠長的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是去撞他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定沒辦法躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝過去的話肯定能把他撞飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被撞飛的樣子  可是相當難見到一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定很具有衝擊性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將會成為傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐美來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謙吾來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission Start！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心  危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A套餐久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相川君  不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮澤謙吾  受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼新玩法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是恭介那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個傷腦筋的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有歹人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  是剛才那個失禮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到事情的部分經過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是宮澤大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…宮澤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次會再考慮得周到一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們幫我這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  你有談過戀愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得之所以會失敗是因為我們沒經歷過戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛不是幸福的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是很痛苦的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相思病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如其名  就像是疾病一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要放棄卻無法放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會一直痛苦下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的指令是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治好相思病
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒寫要成全他倆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要硬去撮合他倆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要治好他單相思的痛苦就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹  我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三番兩次地到底是想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部？  那個失禮的傢伙也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以希望你能原諒他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  能…能把你的信箱地址告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你想要和我成為朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是另外一個人想要和你成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他直接來和我說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那傢伙一看到你就會揪心的痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還會經常想你每天在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿腦子裡都是你  學習也學不進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話  我不太明白這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那傢伙  看起來真的很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹瀨…渣渣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹瀨川佐佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不關我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「心痛」的感覺我倒是能夠體會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這兒等著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿手機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹來川渣渣美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是笹瀨川佐佐美！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是佐佐美的信箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是每天只能發一封哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多的話要等你們關係更近一些後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後除了發郵件以外  盡量別去一直想她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習也給我好好去學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就算是解決了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就看他的表現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過鈴你已經把能做的都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴有朝一日會不會也喜歡上別人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球速變回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再把貓咪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許欺負小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還什麼都沒幹…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐川佐佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是笹瀨佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹瀨川佐佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己不也咬到舌頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  又來鬧事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事情想問你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以告訴我宮澤大人喜歡吃什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙真有女人緣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴她是「不倒湯直接吃的速食炒麵」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不倒湯直接吃的速食炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不倒湯真是太環保了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣會是怎樣的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有吃過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒吃過  再說這是真人騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然又耍我
