Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們  給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:47.10,up,NTP,0,0,0,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.08,up,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又開始了
